本的bra，但其實舊肉無大到</blockquote><br />\n咁有咩問題？呢個牌子係跟佢自己既scale</blockquote><br />\n樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算舊肉無大 帶得耐都會個形靚啲<br />\n<br />\n非打手 打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我著左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夫妻同心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打bodibra洗完易唔易變形？質地好唔好？知唔知body bra出到咩cup？如果台灣f轉做bodibra大概咩cup？</blockquote><br />\n其實任何bra買左四至六個月就要轉 唔好諗住有d bra金剛罩咁可以著幾年<br />\n我自己係幾個月就轉 所以答唔到你易唔易變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質地ok既 我有次試過買左返去條鐵線穿左出黎 佢都免費幫我維修<br />\n唔知出到咩cup 係間鋪見到有d大肥婆咁大果d唔知係咩cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nF應該係轉J cup</blockquote><br />\n不過呢間野幾hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBodibra係咪全部都係全罩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講多數要著番件馬甲先有效果<br />\n如果H cup以上係咪要成6百幾蚊一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222e4851f22b56d8331b840d1d7afd51b67803f7","tid":405153,"uid":126638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咁有咩問題？呢個牌子係跟佢自己既scale</blockquote><br />\n樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算舊肉無大 帶得耐都會個形靚啲<br />\n<br />\n非打手 打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我著左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夫妻同心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打bodibra洗完易唔易變形？質地好唔好？知唔知body bra出到咩cup？如果台灣f轉做bodibra大概咩cup？</blockquote><br />\n其實任何bra買左四至六個月就要轉 唔好諗住有d bra金剛罩咁可以著幾年<br />\n我自己係幾個月就轉 所以答唔到你易唔易變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質地ok既 我有次試過買左返去條鐵線穿左出黎 佢都免費幫我維修<br />\n唔知出到咩cup 係間鋪見到有d大肥婆咁大果d唔知係咩cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nF應該係轉J cup</blockquote><br />\n不過呢間野幾hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBodibra係咪全部都係全罩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講多數要著番件馬甲先有效果<br />\n如果H cup以上係咪要成6百幾蚊一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知係咪全部全罩式呀 不過佢主打包哂d肉 應該多數都係啦<br />\n<br />\n我買過一件馬甲但完全冇心機著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我買個款$7xx呀 不過佢好衰 我覺得佢係專登標高個價然後sell你比大舊錢做會員買平d <br />\n有d取巧"},{"pid":"073e9c7eff92f0aba090003f9314a054384583b3","tid":405153,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咦我用mm前都有著過佢<br />\n但後尾我覺得我個size得好少款</blockquote><br />\n絲打你都係著qmomo f以上？有興趣呀問下都好</blockquote><br />\nmm著落舒服過qmomo？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nQmomo size偏細，減返2個cup就啱"},{"pid":"c189ed490c6b2f33a866824dabd4371b03034ac5","tid":405153,"uid":75297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咦我用mm前都有著過佢<br />\n但後尾我覺得我個size得好少款</blockquote><br />\n絲打你都係著qmomo f以上？有興趣呀問下都好</blockquote><br />\nmm著落